BTTAdditionalActions.BTTPredefinedActionName: Close currently open Touch Bar group

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: if application "Spotify" is running then	tell application "Spotify"		if player state = playing then			set tM to round (((duration of current track) / 1000) / 60) rounding down			set tS to round (((duration of current track) / 1000) mod 60) rounding down						set myTime to ((tM as text) & ":" & tS as text)			set myTrack to name of current track			set myArtist to artist of current track						set myInfo to (myTrack & " by " & myArtist)			return myInfo		else			return "Spotify not playing"		end if	end tellelse	return "Spotify not running"end if
